---

**Project Summary:**
The Employee Recognition Application is a Power Platform solution for digital employee recognition, automated approvals, and secure data management at the Edward Hines Jr. VA Hospital. It features:
- Power Apps Canvas App for award submissions and management
- Automated triage and approval workflows (Power Automate)
- Secure SharePoint integration for data and audit trails
- Professional documentation and user training materials

All code and documentation are licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

